<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us | Republic Surprise</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #fef6e4;
        --card: #ffffff;
        --accent: #ff9f1c;
        --accent-2: #2ec4b6;
        --text: #172b4d;
        --muted: #5f6c7b;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, sans-serif;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 18% 18%, #ffd6a5 0, rgba(255,214,165,0) 32%), radial-gradient(circle at 78% 0%, #a0e8af 0, rgba(160,232,175,0) 32%), var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 72px 16px 64px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .card {
        width: min(640px, 100%);
        background: var(--card);
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 28px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      }
      h1 { margin: 0 0 10px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
      p { margin: 0 0 16px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
      .pill {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        background: #fff3d6;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #b45309;
      }
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .bubble {
        background: #fffaf2;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        text-align: left;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      }
      .bubble h3 {
        margin: 0 0 6px;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }
      .bubble p {
        margin: 0;
      }
      .emoji {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      header, footer {
        position: fixed;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        padding: 14px 18px;
        text-align: center;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
        backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
        color: var(--text);
      }
      header { top: 0; }
      footer { bottom: 0; }
      header h2, footer p { margin: 0; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <div class="card">
      <h1>About Republic Surprise</h1>
      <p>We‚Äôre a playful marketplace for collectible toys and blind boxes, bringing curated drops, easy on-chain checkout, and friendly delivery together so every unboxing feels like a surprise worth sharing.</p>
      <div class="pill">‚ú® Transparent from order to delivery</div>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="bubble">
          <h3><span class="emoji">üîç</span> Traceable orders</h3>
          <p>Every order is logged immutably. You can follow status changes without wondering if anything was altered along the way.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bubble">
          <h3><span class="emoji">üîó</span> Blockchain over black boxes</h3>
          <p>Instead of a traditional database you can‚Äôt inspect, we anchor key events on-chain to prove authenticity of inventory, payments, and confirmations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bubble">
          <h3><span class="emoji">üõ°Ô∏è</span> Shared trust, lower disputes</h3>
          <p>Customers, admins, and delivery partners rely on the same verifiable history. That means fewer disputes, faster resolution, and happier collectors.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bubble">
          <h3><span class="emoji">üåà</span> Cute, careful packaging</h3>
          <p>We pair the tech with friendly service‚Äîbright packaging, careful handling, and clear updates so your parcel arrives just as you expect.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:16px;">
        <a href="/shopping" style="text-decoration:none; background:var(--accent); color:#0f172a; padding:12px 16px; border-radius:12px; font-weight:700; box-shadow:0 12px 24px rgba(255,159,28,0.35); display:inline-block;">Check Out Our Items</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
